[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      138[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Amazon ElastiCache (Redis) for interaction result caching.** Many interaction checks are repeated frequently (common drug combinations in a hospital formulary). Caching scored interaction results for stable medication pairs avoids redundant graph traversals. Cache invalidation triggers when the underlying graph is updated with new source data. Enable Redis AUTH token (rotated via Secrets Manager) so that only authorized Lambda functions can read cached clinical data. The interaction-engine Lambda retrieves the AUTH token from Secrets Manager at cold start.
